      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5274362/" class="title-link">唐振常：纵贯横通论晚清——石泉《甲午战前三十...</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5274362"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/mtyfc/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4644860-53.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/mtyfc/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">月眠</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-01-18"
      class="main-meta">2012-01-18 23:11:27</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5274362_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                         甲午一战，败于蕞尔岛国之日本，而且，败得那样地惨。自是年六月廿三日（公历7 月25 日）接战，至年底，日军连陷平壤、安东、九连城、金州、旅大、盖平，中国军队几无回手之力。翌年乙未三月二十三日（公历4 月17日），签订了丧权辱国至极的《马关条约》。同年五月（公...

